Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While you're watching Kaleido Star,\Nkeep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. I've finally\Nbounced back, everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You see, I remembered how fun that day was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I remembered my policy: {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, I'll be super lucky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just gotta do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll walk straight through the middle of myself,\Nand become a real Kaleido Star! I will! I will!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:09.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:16.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:24.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:32.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:38.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:42.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:02:02.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:17.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point even if you come back,\Nthere's no place for you on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your contract's been terminated too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the obvious choice for me to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let me come back, I'll do anything.\NI won't ask to be paid, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do love Kaleido Stage. Please, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that set on being an unpaid\Ngofer, I've got no reason to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the same as the first time I came to\NKaleido Stage by myself, to do the audition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fresh start from zero. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That time, my dream was\Nto become a Kaleido Star,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this time it's a show\Neveryone can enjoy, with no battles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It might take time, but the path to being\Na true star will open up for me too, I know it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea or coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's asking you if you'd like some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the tea.\NHow about a stylish cocktail or...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no thank you, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on a trip by yourself,\Neven though you're so young?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Oh, yes. But I've got a\Nlot of friends in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? That's nice.\NFriends are so important, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! They're all my really,\Nreally, really good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... I'm not starting from zero.\NI've got everyone with me now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"My Amazing Fresh Start."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Over here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Good to have you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman, I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand\Nyoung people these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, sorry about that. I was just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming to pick me up, Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for\Nyou to get back home, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of what happened I figured\Nout that I really, really love Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should say that stuff in front\Nof everyone who's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I want to create a Kaleido Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the audience and\Nthe cast can all have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it when people smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Sora, I was really worried, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what I'd\Ndo if you never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming all\Nthe way to Japan for me, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken! You went to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just me. I was with Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair! Where are our Japan souvenirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Souvenirs, souvenirs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Miss Sarah, a Ninja Transformation Kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Mia, a good-luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Marion and Jonathan, {\i1}hagoita {\i0}paddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Ken, a globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A globe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Anna, a jester's mask and a slap fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, this thing has kind of a scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Japanese lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Marion, she says this is a lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you really okay now?\NYou're recovered and everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I guess I made everyone worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose sight of my dream anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I got a globe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that's only useful two or\Nthree times in a person's whole life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you don't miss if it's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To you, I give this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be the fool and I'll be\Nthe straight man! This'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I told you\NI'm not going to pair up with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloodlust! I sense bloodlust from someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear a word she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's barking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this glass is really soundproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy Warp Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on winning\Nthe Circus Festival, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if her contract's been\Nterminated, Sora's one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even say "welcome back"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Welcome back"?! Oh please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go onstage, and there's\Nnot even a room for you in the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we were going to\Nexplain that after the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I guess that makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You'll be a guest in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,okay Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means this is no time\Nfor you to be here partying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go see the Boss already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get him to\Nlet you back on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because in my book, the festival isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically she wants Sora to be back onstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't she just\Ncome right out and say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to beat you\Nfair and square, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm fine with the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided not to fight\Nbattles anymore, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying... you don't\Nintend to go back onstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't given up on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely want to go back onstage someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to do battle onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work with\Neveryone to create a fun show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my dream right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be working for you all from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you want anything\Ndone, please just give me a yell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute to curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay everybody, stay\Non top of things today too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make especially sure you give it all\Nyou've got during the Demon Spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the scenes after that\Nwith the two of us in them. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you are fired up enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want Sora to go back onstage, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora decided this for herself,\Nso let's support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get this set piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, got it, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might've been a little too heavy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone deliver these costumes quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, got it, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you do this, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this one to passage 3B
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this one to passage 2C.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Mr. Leon and May as Romeo and Juliet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, Kaleido Stage\Nbelongs to May and Mr. Leon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the costumes here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I prepared myself for that. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in the end... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm jealous of May and the\Napplause she's being showered with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kinda bad for having you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting to see lots of parts of\NKaleido Stage I didn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know lots more about Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love Kaleido Stage, don't you Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall in love with it more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, so this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told the people who messed up\Nthe lighting today to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon was watching Sora. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's green.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Japanese tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, I don't know\Nif you'll like it, but I hope so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drink it. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get used to\Nthis stuff, it's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't really get\Nwhy you don't want to battle onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still proud of the time when I was aiming\Nto win consecutive world championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But according to you, is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's not what I think at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you're amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I think May was great\Nwhen she won the festival too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just figured out that those\Nweren't my dreams, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I dream of\Nbeing onstage with you, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'm definitely\Ngoing to go back to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a show with you?\NI'd like to do that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you want more tea I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La dadi dadi dadi dadi dadi dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The oats have made a good harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La dadi dadi dadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The green peas have made a good harvest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any bad children around?\NAre there any sleepyheads around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who asked me to wake you\Nup quietly so Rosetta wouldn't wake up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I have cleaning\Nduty first thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll just cuddle\Nup with Rosetta and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I have something important to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Layla! Layla's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you, telling lies\Nabout Miss Layla. That's so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm telling you, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't manage to tell you before,\Nbut according to my fortunetelling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla's constellation, Leo, is very close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll tell you flat-out,\Nyesterday was boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't make me feel a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The individual stunts may be attention-grabbers,\Nbut the thing as a whole isn't a coherent show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it's like a bunch of\None-man shows jumbled together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, let's hear your opinion as the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, this is Cathy Timor.\NShe's a noted off-Broadway director.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm just a layman\Noutside my area of expertise,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just gave you my honest feelings about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm sorry. I think\NMiss Cathy is absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't able to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault. It's all\Nmy fault. I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I fired? I am fired, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Miss Cathy is here. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'll admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... "Demon Spiral,"\Nwasn't that what it was called?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making that work within Romeo\Nand Juliet, that's not a bad concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The character adaptations are chic too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a setup, I think it's quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is your directing ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now our attendance rate isn't dropping,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the demographics of the\Naudience are drastically unbalanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like your help correcting that trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take on this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now that that's settled, let's go, Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "huh?" me. I'm an outsider here,\Nso it won't work if you're not there, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, that's no good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon and May, your timing\Nwasn't in synch at all right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you so off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's because in performance\NMay can't get very much height,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so when Mr. Leon compensates,\Nhis maneuver ends up looking small,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that's why it looks--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience doesn't care about stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, May, come here a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, I get that your skill is\Namazing and everything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So show me something that\Nmakes my heart pound more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, your performance in New York\Nmade my blood thrum in my veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what was {\i1}with {\i0}you just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, a Romeo who's\Nsatisfied as long as he's shining
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a Juliet who's terrified of being hated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to get anyone excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take your audience lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, take five!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's not anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she said she had\Ncleaning duty this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla's here and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what it looks like. I'm wiping the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This part was a little smudged,\Nand it just started bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind about that, Miss Layla is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from Broadway\Nnamed Cathy is with her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Cathy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... but at the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said to me,\Nso I don't know how to face Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hesitating and stopping\Nshort over every little thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sora I know tries it\Nrather than thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you mean to never see\NMiss Layla again for your whole life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have a chance too, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A chance to go back to the stage... But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, play it back for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, even you can tell, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this listless performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like right here, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show us that bit one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rewind about thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you aren't trying\Nto look at each other at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's never been a pair of lovers like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can just sneak a look and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look, it {\i1}is {\i0}Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would you come down here for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you do Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not contracted\Nanymore, but just give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Sora? You've gotten\Nyour chance right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, even if you want to avoid the battle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it looks like the people around\Nyou aren't going to let that happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos won't complain. There's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, let's see it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see your Juliet! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue with May as Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you don't want to battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just running away\Nfrom the competition, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should think carefully about how\Nmuch your attitude just now hurt May.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when you can\Nhurt someone by not fighting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let what happened\Ntoday get to you too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cheer everyone up\Njust by being around, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're not onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can just do what you think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ken, are you coming or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to become my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my goals are different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of a stage without any\Nbattling might be just a fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no matter how hard it is,\NI want to make that real!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I told you to become my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, you're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who can become my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe, Mr. Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie... I'm so glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sora, Mr. Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one after all, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? Why did he call Sora "Sophie"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who's "Sophie"? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:49.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:53.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:02.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:08.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:10.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:12.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:16.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Escape for the sake of tomorrow {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:22.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I don't have a vacation, I've got an oasis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:29.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn off the cell phone and charge my love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:34.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because some pain,\Nyou can't soothe with just kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:38.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone, we pass each other by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:39.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:45.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the far end of regret,\NI encounter my true heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:53.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether I'm crying or\Nlaughing, I will be with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:57.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Kaleido Star: New Wings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:24:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person who can become\Nmy partner is Sora Naegino.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, my goal is a stage without battles!{\i0}
